<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Kitzmiller_v._Dover_Area_School_District&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Defendants">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Defendants</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Dover Area School District</li>
<li>Dover Area School District Board of Directors</li>
</ul>
<dl>
